TextEng: "Where is the Knower of Names imprisoned?"
"You just don't want to tell me!"
"No, but I had hoped you would."
"Tell me about your sister, the Knower of Names."
"She let herself be loved by Mephistopheles?"
"I love you for more than just your mind..."
Text: "난 네 정신뿐 아니라 그 이상을 사랑해..."

TextEng: "I don't know what you're talking about."
